ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2003-2004
PrecisAppointment of NICHOLAS COGHLAN as Consul General of Canada at Cape Town, Republic of South Africa; DENIS COMEAU as Ambassador of Canada to the Lao People's Democratic Republic, with residence in Bangkok; LOUIS-ROBERT DAIGLE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Mozambique; LOUISE MARCHAND as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Cape Verde, and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Gambia, with residence in Dakar; and JOHN McNEE as Ambassador of Canada to the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg, with residence in Brussels.
